00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:24,580
Sepertinya terjadi sesuatu di stasiun TV ini.

328
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:27,082
-Apa? -Di stasiun TV ini?

329
00:19:32,788 --> 00:19:34,390
Apa itu?

330
00:19:34,390 --> 00:19:35,391
Ya?

